The way to do this is to use a `Pipeline`.  The general idea is you define the pipeline and give it a name on your cluster.  Then you can reference it when indexing data and the data you send will be passed through that pipeline to transform it.  Note pipelines will only run on nodes marked as &quot;ingest&quot; nodes.

