The [`MutationObserver` API][1] is the recommended way to watch DOM modifications. It&#39;s easy to integrate, too.

Be sure to inspect the `mutation` variable, to get an idea what kind of information you can access.

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

